## UPS Alert!

{{#is_warning}}
UPS is running on **battery power** — mains power has been lost!
Check your power supply immediately.
{{/is_warning}}

{{#is_alert}}
UPS battery is **critically low** — system may shut down soon!
Take action immediately.
{{/is_alert}}

{{#is_recovery}}
UPS has returned to mains power.
{{/is_recovery}}

